_json.gridTitle: How to Create a Spiritual Growth Plan (5 Steps) - Vibrant Christian Living
_json.description: Does growing spiritually seem like a mystery or something reserved for “other people”? You know that there’s got to be something more than just living for what this life offers, but you’re not sure how to get there. Maybe you even go to church on Sunday and pray before meals… but still you feel like something’s missing or lacking. Friend, I want to tell you that what you’re feeling is not only normal, but it’s a beautiful invitation to grow deeper with God! God loves you and wants to show yo...
